Wizards of High Sorcery
=======================

Structure
---------
The Wizards of High Sorcery (WoHS) are an occupational mage guild, based on
a similar 'guild' in the Dragonlance series of books by Margaret Weis
and Tracy Hickman. However, they will be treated like three sub-guilds,
ruled by a mortal council (Conclave) of the highest member of each
sub-guild.

Each sub-guild has its own spells and skills. 
The three sub-guilds are divided by a simple quality, alignment.
White-robed Mages are good in alignment, from numerically +400->+1200 align.
Red-robed Mages are neutral in alignment, from numerically -400->+400 align.
Black-robed Mages are evil in alignment, from numerically -400->-1200 align. 

Guildmaster:
------------
The guildmaster of this guild is Rastlin.

